            <h1>In Response to the NSA, We Need A New Church Committee and We Need It Now</h1>
    </div>
<div class="panel-pane pane-eff-content-type">
            DEEPLINKS BLOG    </div>
<div class="panel-pane pane-eff-author">
            <div class="byline">By <a href="/about/staff/cindy-cohn">Cindy Cohn</a> and Trevor Timm</div><div class="date">June 7, 2013</div>    </div>
  </div>

<!-- See if there's anything in the banner -->
  <div class="banner-wrapper">
    <div class="panel-pane pane-banner">
