</div>              <h3 class="node__title"><a href="/deeplinks/2020/03/earn-it-act-violates-constitution" rel="bookmark">The EARN IT Act Violates the Constitution</a></h3>
            
    </header>
  
  
  <div class="node__content">
    <div class="eff-translation-links"></div><div class="field field--name-body field--type-text-with-summary field--label-hidden"><div class="field__items"><div class="field__item even">Since senators introduced the <a href="https://www.congress.gov/bill/116th-congress/senate-bill/3398/text">EARN IT Act (S. 3398)</a> in early March, EFF has called attention to the many ways in which the bill would be a <a href="https://www.eff.org/deeplinks/2020/03/graham-blumenthal-bill-attack-online-speech-and-security">disaster</a> for Internet users’ <a href="https://www.eff.org/deeplinks/2020/03/graham-blumenthal-bill-attack-online-speech-and-security">free speech and security</a>. We’ve explained how the EARN IT Act could be used to <a>...</a></div></div></div>  </div>

